{"tid":1507482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家小心，今日跳閘果陣俾個藍絲偷拍仲跟蹤","createTime":"2019-08-26T07:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T07:45:04.000Z","uid":288788,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1bbf4e77519a948369b37dfeaaa6c8ff0051bb","tid":1507482,"uid":288788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:22:50.000Z","msg":"今日打算響應跳閘運動，點知真係無乜人跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾個藍絲師奶見到，佢由上車一直啤到我落車，期間仲好似一直偷拍，仲跟埋我落車跟住我係咁打電話俾人。感覺應該係黑警既家屬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我兜咗個大圈上上落落月台先放甩左佢。<br />\n<br />\n大家跳閘果陣真係要小心藍絲會唔知做啲乜，佢啲眼神好得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n附圖。。我太仁慈 唔敢影佢樣。。。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sXTP9B5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsXTP9B5.jpg&h=7e55a567&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e70be730cc80690d87c0c7528a8248d5291c26a5","tid":1507482,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:23:06.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=adc54933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"23e30cdca4745e1ee1e47ba491b35b04fb709b2d","tid":1507482,"uid":185990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:23:43.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=